Detailed Description

BoxContainer iterator picking items with a specified owner rank.

This iterator runs through all Boxes in a BoxContainer that has the given owner rank. The iterator runs through the Boxes in the order they appear in the BoxContainer, skipping over Boxes that do not have the specified owner rank.
